OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fat first before cloud in the west
OL,7,Fspreads eastwards across the region by
OL,8,Fthe morning. However, it should remain
OL,9,Fgenerally dry. Winds mainly light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first but
OL,12,Fsunny spells spells developing through
OL,13,Fthe day. Winds generally light, with
OL,14,Ftemperatures slightly lower than
OL,15,FFriday, but still very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
